title: Broom in the Tree
filterKeywords: nicky kennedy broom in the tree event planning
description:
Making dreams come true

In this series, you get to listen in on conversations with renowned experts in all aspects of event management.

Nicky Kennedy's guests share with you their stories, their memories, their tips, tricks, and even some behind-the-scenes insights so that your next event, from a candle-lit dinner to a wedding for thousands, creates beautiful memories.
